title: Top celebrity travel pictures of the week
text:
Top celebrity travel pictures of the week Last updated 14:02, October 8 2015 JustinBieber/Instagram TaylorSwift/Instagram Selena/GomezInstagram LillyRoseDepp/Instagram KendalJenner/nstagram KatyPerryInstagram Instagram Rihanna /Instagram LadyGaga/Instagram MariaSharapovaInstagram KourtneyKardashian/Instagram 
After a whirlwind tour of Australia and New Zealand, its time for Justin Bieber to chill in beautiful Bora Bora. 
What to do when you are Taylor Swift and you can't take your cat on your travels? You make a giant cut out of it instead! 
Singer Selena Gomez enjoying some "me" time in an undisclosed place. 
Lilly-Rose Depp (daughter of Johnny Depp) rocks some Statue of Liberty themed sunglasses while out shopping with her mum. 
When in Paris, do what Kendal Jenner did and go to a football game! 
Last week it was Peru, this week its Chile for jet-setter Katy Perry. 
Victoria Secret Girls just wanna have fun in the sun. Which they are doing in Palm Beach, US. 
Rihanna sizzles in Brazil. 
Lady Gaga shows off her enviable pins in New York. 
Tennis player Maria Sharapova enjoying the sights and sounds of Paris. 
Kourtney Kardashian takes this super cute picture with her son Regin in Yellowstone Park. 1 of 11 « Previous « Previous Next » Next » 
Celebrities always seem to be on holiday. Checkout some of their top travel pictures of the week.
